SUMMARY:Crum Woods Walk
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Scott Arboretum'\, 'Be Well']\\nCategory: Train
 ing/Workshop\\nJoin us for a morning walk through the Crum Woods.  We'll 
 start at the bottom of the Scott Amphitheater and walk approximately one m
 ile to the Matchbox. Please wear sturdy shoes and bring a water bottle.  
 This is not a fast walk\, but we will be on uneven terrain and walking up 
 and down the hills. No need to sign up.  \\nDetails: https://swatcentral.
 swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1396675799
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1396675799
