 bit\\nSwarthmore College Libraries marks "America250" with a special exhib
 ition in McCabe Library. Drawing on art and artifacts from Special Collect
 ions\, the exhibition explores how family\, land\, and nation have shaped 
 the idea of “America\,” and invites visitors to consider how they see 
 this country and its history today. \\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swart
 hmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1390576097
LOCATION:McCabe Library Atrium Exhibits
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1390576097
