SUMMARY:Hatha Yoga with Stacy Bomento
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Recreation & Wellness']\\nCategory: Recreation-
 General\\nThis Hatha yoga class will focus on breathing and mindful moveme
 nt\, helping to increase strength and flexibility. Offering modifications 
 for various postures\, this class is accessible to all levels of practice.
  Each practice will include poses\, breathing exercises\, and a restorativ
 e and calming finish\, followed by guided meditation. **There will be no c
 lass on July 23**\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmb
 ed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1391945957
